@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram - Online Quiz System

[*] --> Login

state Login <<choice>>
Login --> Register : [Register]
Login --> TeacherLogin : [Teacher Login]
Login --> StudentLogin : [Student Login]

state "Register" as Register
Register : entry / start state
Register : do / enter details
Register : exit / registration complete

state "Teacher Login" as TeacherLogin
TeacherLogin : entry / enter teacher credentials
TeacherLogin : do / verify credentials
TeacherLogin : exit / logged in as teacher

state "Student Login" as StudentLogin
StudentLogin : entry / enter student credentials
StudentLogin : do / verify credentials
StudentLogin : exit / logged in as student

state TeacherLogin --> TeacherMain <<choice>>

state "Create Quiz" as CreateQuiz
CreateQuiz : entry / choose to create quiz
CreateQuiz : do / create new quiz
CreateQuiz : exit / quiz created

state "Edit Quiz" as EditQuiz
EditQuiz : entry / choose to edit quiz
EditQuiz : do / edit existing quiz
EditQuiz : exit / quiz edited

state "Save Quiz" as SaveQuiz
SaveQuiz : entry / choose to save quiz
SaveQuiz : do / save quiz as draft
SaveQuiz : exit / quiz saved as draft

state "Post Quiz" as PostQuiz
PostQuiz : entry / choose to post quiz
PostQuiz : do / post quiz for students
PostQuiz : exit / quiz posted

state "View Quiz Results" as ViewResults
ViewResults : entry / choose to view results
ViewResults : do / view quiz results
ViewResults : exit / results viewed

state TeacherMain --> CreateQuiz
TeacherMain --> EditQuiz
TeacherMain --> SaveQuiz
TeacherMain --> PostQuiz
TeacherMain --> ViewResults

state StudentLogin --> StudentMain <<choice>>

state "Select Quiz" as SelectQuiz
SelectQuiz : entry / notified to select quiz
SelectQuiz : do / select quiz
SelectQuiz : exit / quiz selected

state "Answer Quiz" as AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz : entry / start answering quiz
AnswerQuiz : do / answer questions
AnswerQuiz : exit / quiz answered

state "Submit Quiz" as SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz : entry / choose to submit quiz
SubmitQuiz : do / submit quiz
SubmitQuiz : exit / quiz submitted

state "View Result" as ViewResult
ViewResult : entry / choose to view result
ViewResult : do / view quiz result
ViewResult : exit / result viewed

state StudentMain --> SelectQuiz
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult

state "Final State" as FinalState
FinalState : entry / final state

@enduml
